properties.name: AK O'Conner
properties.description: Posted by Jwagnerdsm 4050 Urbandale Ave, Des Moines, IA, 50310Live music many nights, including Sundays when Jason Walsmith hosts his friends for great sounds. Good beer selection, hip crowd, good kitchen serving grilled foods.

properties.name: B & B Restaurant & Bar
properties.description: Posted by Jwagnerdsm 2712 Beaver Ave, Des Moines, IA, 50310(515) 255-8521 A neighborhood favorite in the heart of Beaverdale with smoked meats, fish tacos, a fine wine list and a terrific patio on the roof.

properties.name: Beaverdale Pizza
properties.description: Posted by Jwagnerdsm 2713 Beaver Avenue, Des Moines, IA, 50310Unusual pizza recipe that fans swear by. We like the gyros and other Bosnian fare. And check out the grocery store featuring Eastern European foods.

properties.name: Chef's Kitchen
properties.description: Posted by Jwagnerdsm 1903 Beaver Ave, Des Moines, IA(515) 255-4411 Upscale cooking served in a semi-casual environment. Regular winner of "Best of Des Moines Awards." Don\'t miss the homemade cookies on your way out.

properties.name: Christopher's
properties.description: Posted by Jwagnerdsm 2816 Beaver Ave, Des Moines, IA, 50310Where Beaverdale residents have celebrated special events for two generations. Great steaks, pasta, pizza, seafood, and a fine lounge to visit friends or watch a game.

properties.name: Cooney's Tavern
properties.description: Posted by Jwagnerdsm  3708 Beaver Ave, Des Moines, Iowa, 50310Beaverdale\'s answer to Cheers, a genial place where the bartender will remember your name and your drink. Nice selection of beer, Irish whiskey, etc.

properties.name: Flying Mango
properties.description: Posted by Jwagnerdsm 4345 Hickman Rd, Des Moines, IA, 50310(515) 255-4111 Cajun, Caribbean, and barbecue at this funky,fun restaurant on the edge of the Beaverdale neighborhood.

properties.name: GoodSons Martini and Panini
properties.description: Posted by Jwagnerdsm 2821 Beaver Ave Des MoinesNew joint in "downtown" area that features martinis and paninis, fireplaces and wood paneled walls.

properties.name: Grounds for Celebration
properties.description: Posted by Jwagnerdsm 2645 Beaver Ave, Des Moines, IA, 50310A terrific coffee shop with free Wi-Fi and lots of pastry, sandwiches and other goodies. Homemade Gelato in the summer, too.

properties.name: Kelley's
properties.description: Posted by Jwagnerdsm 3606 Beaver Ave. - Des Moines A popular bar the skews toward a younger crowd who vie for a turn on the pool table or video games, watch sports on TV, and drink in the parking lot patio.

properties.name: Mandarin Chinese Restaurant
properties.description: Posted by Jwagnerdsm 3520 Beaver Ave, Des Moines, IA, 50310(515) 277-6263 Long regarded as one of the city\'s best Chinese restaurants, nothing has changed in that regard.

properties.name: Michaels Restaurant & Lounge
properties.description: Posted by Jwagnerdsm 4041 Urbandale Ave, Des Moines, IA, 50310(515) 255-9894 This still feels like the old roadhouse it once was and the food is all homemade. Try the famous Breaded Pork Tenderloin, the broasted chicken, or the biscuits and gravy. Everything here is spot on.

properties.name: Poor Michaels Pizza & Carry Out
properties.description: Posted by Jwagnerdsm 4039 Urbandale Ave, Des Moines, IA, 50310(515) 255-5959 Thin-crust pizza with top-notch ingredients and unusual combinations. The Reuben and the combo are neighborhood favorites. No delivery but if you draw the straw to pick up dinner, the counter man will give you a slice of pizza to eat on the way home.

properties.name: Rice Bowl
properties.description: Posted by Jwagnerdsm 2607 Beaver Ave, Des Moines, IA, 50310(515) 255-0165 Another Beaverdale icon, an longstanding Chinese restaurant where neighborhood kids got their first taste of egg rolls and lo mein

properties.name: Snookies
properties.description: Posted by Jwagnerdsm 1810 Beaver Ave, Des Moines, IA, 50310(515) 255-0638 Where Beaverdale families gather on warm nights. Open seasonally and home to traditional ice cream treats and simple sandwiches. Our dogs love the free cones that are provided to canines.

properties.name: Taste of China
properties.description: Posted by Jwagnerdsm 4212 Douglas Ave Ste A, Des Moines, IA, 50310(515) 277-2222 A Taste of China? Maybe closer to the menu you\'d find on a street stand in Hong Kong, but delicious just the same.

properties.name: Tasty Tacos
properties.description: Posted by Jwagnerdsm 3715 Douglas Ave, Des Moines, IA, 50310(515) 274-0884 Famous for their flour tacos, there are Tasty Tacos across Des Moines. This is a popular stop for takeout or eat-in.

properties.name: el Aguila Real
properties.description: Posted by Jwagnerdsm 3600 Beaver Ave, Des Moines, IA, 50310Beaverdale residents quickly fell in love with this authentic Mexican restaurant, known for its quick service,homemade chips, moles, vegetarian items and expansive menu.
